believe me.

1015
01:16:39,172 --> 01:16:41,046
But this is going too far.

1016
01:16:41,880 --> 01:16:44,379
- Got it?
- Yes, Mr Wenger.

1017
01:16:50,420 --> 01:16:51,565
Sit down.

1018
01:16:54,482 --> 01:16:58,232
Write down your experiences with "The Wave"
over the past week,

1019
01:16:58,961 --> 01:17:01,148
and put them on my desk
at the end of class.

1020
01:17:05,106 --> 01:17:06,251
Get started.

1021
01:17:36,663 --> 01:17:37,601
Time's up.

1022
01:17:46,037 --> 01:17:47,079
See you later, Mr Wenger.

1023
01:17:47,288 --> 01:17:52,913
This doesn't mean I wouldn't appreciate
seeing you at the game.

1024
01:17:52,913 --> 01:17:54,578
We need your support.

1025
01:18:00,307 --> 01:18:04,265
Mr Wenger, I know who's responsible
for the graffiti on the town hall.

1026
01:18:05,098 --> 01:18:07,702
Tim, did I ask you to tell me who did it?

1027
01:18:08,639 --> 01:18:09,785
I don't want to know.

1028
01:18:09,785 --> 01:18:12,909
If I knew, I'd have to inform
the principal and the police.

1029
01:18:13,222 --> 01:18:14,992
It's called vandalism.

1030
01:18:16,138 --> 01:18:19,992
If you've learnt one thing this week,
it's the value of sticking together.

1031
01:18:20,617 --> 01:18:24,262
You of all people should take that to heart.

1032
01:18:27,490 --> 01:18:29,366
I'll be pleased to see you
at the game today. Okay?

1033
01:18:33,843 --> 01:18:34,678
Okay.

1034
01:19:11,027 --> 01:19:11,859
Come on!

1035
01:19:12,068 --> 01:19:13,630
Yes, now play forward!

1036
01:19:14,255 --> 01:19:16,338
Marco, go forward!
What are you doing?

1037
01:19:19,463 --> 01:19:21,858
Yes! Superb!

1038
01:19:28,108 --> 01:19:30,295
- I can't let you in.
- Why not?

1039
01:19:30,295 --> 01:19:32,065
Get yourself a white shirt,
there are still some left outside.

1040
01:19:32,273 --> 01:19:34,253
I don't want your shitty "Wave" shirt!

1041
01:19:34,565 --> 01:19:36,544
Everybody has one,
don't make a scene.

1042
01:19:36,544 --> 01:19:37,794
You're full of shit!

1043
01:19:38,835 --> 01:19:40,501
The right side is reserved for us.

1044
01:19:41,439 --> 01:19:42,793
You've all gone crazy.

1045
01:19:59,041 --> 01:20:00,187
Defence, get closer!

1046
01:20:03,311 --> 01:20:04,978
Go, forward now! Forward!

1047
01:20:14,976 --> 01:20:17,581
Excellent!

1048
01:20:18,517 --> 01:20:20,705
- What do you say now?
- Shut your mouth!

1049
01:20:21,006 --> 01:20:23,092
No mistakes now! 

1050
01:20:25,080 --> 01:20:26,329
Now what?

1051
01:20:27,787 --> 01:20:29,349
I'm not giving up that easily.

1052
01:20:36,640 --> 01:20:38,723
Fall back! You're ahead!

1053
01:20:43,154 --> 01:20:45,240
Go, Go! Faster! 
Go, Faster! 

1054
01:21:06,948 --> 01:21:08,094
Piss off, man!

1055
01:21:09,760 --> 01:21:10,698
You bastard!

1056
01:21:26,051 --> 01:21:28,084
- Ready?
- Yeah. 

1057
01:21:31,112 --> 01:21:34,341
Stop "The Wave"!

1058
01:21:35,175 --> 01:21:37,258
Stop "The Wave"!

1059
01:21:47,298 --> 01:21:49,056
Had to be them.

1060
01:21:49,485 --> 01:21:51,059
Bring them all to me.

1061
01:21:56,592 --> 01:21:58,787
You're sick, go home! 

1062
01:21:58,952 --> 01:21:59,351
Hey, sit down! 

1063
01:22:13,672 --> 01:22:15,708
What's your problem? 

1064
01:22:17,773 --> 01:22:19,439
What's going on?

1065
01:22:31,104 --> 01:22:32,874
Are you nuts?

1066
01:22:35,374 --> 01:22:36,625
What's wrong with you?

1067
01:22:38,291 --> 01:22:39,437
What are you doing?

1068
01:22:40,791 --> 01:22:42,457
Sinan, what's wrong with you?

1069
01:22:50,268 --> 01:22:52,247
Shit! I just don't believe it. 

1070
01:22:53,289 --> 01:22:55,580
You got them on this trip!

1071
01:22:55,580 --> 01:22:58,080
Was it my idea for them to start a brawl?

1072
01:22:58,080 --> 01:23:01,793
- Of course not.
- What do you mean, then?

1073
01:23:01,793 --> 01:23:05,057
You relish the way they hang on 
your every word.

1074
01:23:05,371 --> 01:23:10,370
Are you telling me you wouldn't?
You're a teacher too.

1075
01:23:10,370 --> 01:23:11,724
That's not the point!

1076
01:23:12,036 --> 01:23:14,849
They look up to you,
but you're manipulating them!

1077
01:23:15,161 --> 01:23:18,077
It's an ego trip.
Don't you see that?

1078
01:23:18,077 --> 01:23:19,327
I think you're jealous.

1079
01:23:19,327 --> 01:23:24,326
- What?
- Because they don't look up to you.

1080
01:23:24,326 --> 01:23:25,889
This minor-league teacher is showing you up.

1081
01:23:25,889 --> 01:23:28,094
You think that's the problem?

1082
01:23:28,094 --> 01:23:30,227
It's what you all think!

1083
01:23:30,227 --> 01:23:33,700
Because of my college, 
physical education and political science.

1084
01:23:34,325 --> 01:23:37,450
- I never knew the wound was so deep.
- Oh, you didn't?

1085
01:23:38,282 --> 01:23:43,075
At least I don't pop pills every Monday
because I'm scared of going to school!

1086
01:23:56,551 --> 01:23:59,259
Anke... Anke, wait...

1087
01:24:01,551 --> 01:24:03,112
- I didn't mean that.
- You did.

1088
01:24:03,634 --> 01:24:04,951
You said it and you meant it.

1089
01:24:04,951 --> 01:24:07,216
You've turned into an asshole.

1090
01:24:08,216 --> 01:24:09,987
Just leave me alone!

1091
01:24:17,272 --> 01:24:18,341
Shit! 

1092
01:24:19,528 --> 01:24:25,151
Karo, what was that back there?
You can't do that! 

1093
01:24:25,151 --> 01:24:26,922
You think you're some kind of resistance fighter?

1094
01:24:26,922 --> 01:24:30,255
What's up with you?
What was the deal at the game?

1095
01:24:30,568 --> 01:24:33,447
- It was full for the first time.
- And the fight?

1096
01:24:33,447 --> 01:24:35,254
That was because of this!

1097
01:24:35,567 --> 01:24:36,922
You just don't get it, do you?

1098
01:24:36,922 --> 01:24:39,213
We'd have won if not for you.

1099
01:24:40,149 --> 01:24:41,609
That bugs you.

1100
01:24:42,024 --> 01:24:43,900
For once it was my show today.

1101
01:24:44,732 --> 01:24:45,670
You moron.

1102
01:24:45,886 --> 01:24:47,232
- Karo!
- Leave me alone! 

1103
01:24:47,232 --> 01:24:49,015
Don't walk away!

1104
01:25:00,251 --> 01:25:01,292
Let go of me!

1105
01:25:02,959 --> 01:25:04,209
- Let go of me!
- Karo. 

1106
01:25:07,334 --> 01:25:08,792
Get lost!

1107
01:25:52,015 --> 01:25:53,265
Marco, what are you doing here?

1108
01:25:55,869 --> 01:25:57,015
I screwed up.

1109
01:25:57,326 --> 01:25:58,368
Come on in.

1110
01:26:02,681 --> 01:26:03,722
What happened?

1111
01:26:08,096 --> 01:26:09,241
I hit Karo.

1112
01:26:10,283 --> 01:26:11,325
You did what?

1113
01:26:12,575 --> 01:26:15,178
- I hit Karo.
- Why?

1114
01:26:16,782 --> 01:26:19,345
I don't know.

1115
01:26:20,491 --> 01:26:22,469
We had a fight about...

1116
01:26:23,928 --> 01:26:26,636
This whole shit has totally changed me!

1117
01:26:27,052 --> 01:26:28,682
I love Karo!

1118
01:26:28,682 --> 01:26:30,973
But I still hit her.

1119
01:26:30,973 --> 01:26:35,176
All this pseudo-discipline,
it's totally fascist!

1120
01:26:36,009 --> 01:26:37,051
You have to stop it.

1121
01:26:39,029 --> 01:26:40,551
Rainer?

1122
01:26:44,029 --> 01:26:45,758
I'll think of something.

1123
01:26:46,696 --> 01:26:47,737
You have to call it off. 

1124
01:26:48,466 --> 01:26:51,174
- Now!
- Don't tell me what to do. 

1125
01:27:06,172 --> 01:27:08,671
Yes, Dr Kohlhage, I know that.

1126
01:27:09,665 --> 01:27:11,667
I know, I know, yes. 

1127
01:27:11,031 --> 01:27:12,942
I won't downplay the seriousness of it.

1128
01:27:14,192 --> 01:27:18,045
I take full responsibility,
but I must speak to the students.

1129
01:27:18,254 --> 01:27:21,067
All I'm asking is for you 
to trust me on this.

1130
01:27:36,689 --> 01:27:38,043
Hey guys, just arrived!

1131
01:27:38,459 --> 01:27:41,479
"Tomorrow, school hall, 12 o'clock.
"The Wave"'s future is at stake."

1132
01:27:41,896 --> 01:27:44,395
"Pass it on only to members and supporters."

1133
01:27:44,605 --> 01:27:45,751
Three exclamation marks?

1134
01:28:27,203 --> 01:28:28,923
SATURDAY

1135
01:28:46,158 --> 01:28:48,450
Mr Wenger, it's quarter past 12.

1136
01:28:49,699 --> 01:28:51,991
Lock the doors.
I don't want any interruptions.

1137
01:28:52,199 --> 01:28:53,137
Yes, sir.

1138
01:28:54,179 --> 01:28:59,699
I'd like to stay standing up here,
so I have a clear view of the room.

1139
01:29:00,219 --> 01:29:01,574
Go ahead.

1140
01:29:09,385 --> 01:29:11,051
All clear here?

1141
01:29:14,384 --> 01:29:15,842
Then lock the doors.

1142
01:29:15,842 --> 01:29:18,863
Mr Wenger doesn't want any interruptions.

1143
01:29:20,216 --> 01:29:21,467
Everyone inside!

1144
01:29:50,966 --> 01:29:54,925
"I always had everything I wanted:
clothes, money, whatever,

1145
01:29:55,837 --> 01:29:57,920
"but what I had most of was boredom."

1146
01:29:58,128 --> 01:29:59,066
That's mine.

1147
01:29:59,378 --> 01:30:01,462
"The last few days have been really fun.

1148
01:30:03,024 --> 01:30:07,190
"It doesn't matter who's the best-looking,
the most popular or successful.

1149
01:30:07,919 --> 01:30:09,690
"The Wave" has made us all equal."

1150
01:30:11,502 --> 01:30:14,835
"Race, religion and class don't matter anymore.

1151
01:30:15,772 --> 01:30:17,334
"We all belong to a movement.

1152
01:30:18,064 --> 01:30:22,542
"The Wave" gives our lives meaning,
ideals worth standing up for."

1153
01:30:23,271 --> 01:30:24,729
"I used to bully other students,

1154
01:30:25,145 --> 01:30:28,062
"but the more I think about it,
the lamer it seems.

1155
01:30:28,478 --> 01:30:30,978
"It's much better to be part of a good cause."

1156
01:30:32,019 --> 01:30:35,457
"If we all rely on each other,
we can accomplish so much more,

1157
01:30:35,873 --> 01:30:38,060
"even if it means personal sacrifices."

1158
01:30:43,268 --> 01:30:44,831
As you surely noticed,

1159
01:30:45,247 --> 01:30:49,414
they were excerpts from your essays
about the past week.

1160
01:30:51,038 --> 01:30:53,226
It's impressive,
what you got out of "The Wave".

1161
01:30:53,642 --> 01:30:56,662
We shouldn't just allow our project to end.

1162
01:31:01,037 --> 01:31:03,745
- Rainer, what the hell?
- Marco, sit down!

1163
01:31:03,745 --> 01:31:05,828
Yes, but... People think...

1164
01:31:06,037 --> 01:31:07,494
I said sit down!

1165
01:31:11,139 --> 01:31:13,119
Germany's been going downhill for years.

1166
01:31:13,639 --> 01:31:15,410
We're the losers of globalisation,

1167
01:31:15,826 --> 01:31:20,201
but the politicians want us to believe
the only solution is to work harder.

1168
01:31:21,138 --> 01:31:23,534
But the politicians
are puppets for big business!

1169
01:31:24,159 --> 01:31:28,429
They say unemployment's falling,
and we're still the world's export champions.

1170
01:31:28,950 --> 01:31:33,844
But in reality, the poor are getting poorer
and the rich, richer!

1171
01:31:36,969 --> 01:31:39,157
Our greatest threat is terror.

1172
01:31:40,511 --> 01:31:42,698
A terror we unleashed ourselves,

1173
01:31:42,908 --> 01:31:46,345
because of the injustice we permit 
in the world!

1174
01:31:46,656 --> 01:31:49,885
And while we slowly destroy our planet,

1175
01:31:50,822 --> 01:31:53,426
a few of the superwealthy rub their hands

1176
01:31:53,946 --> 01:31:57,696
and build themselves spaceships
so they can watch from above!

1177
01:32:00,612 --> 01:32:04,570
Don't you see what he's doing?
He's manipulating you.

1178
01:32:04,778 --> 01:32:05,820
Marco, sit down!

1179
01:32:06,132 --> 01:32:08,528
You can't stop me speaking the truth, Marco.

1180
01:32:08,841 --> 01:32:10,507
"The Wave" is the real problem!

1181
01:32:12,174 --> 01:32:16,651
No. "The Wave" is the only answer.

1182
01:32:17,069 --> 01:32:18,735
Together, we can do anything.

1183
01:32:20,610 --> 01:32:21,652
We...

1184
01:32:23,629 --> 01:32:27,379
We have the opportunity to make history!

1185
01:32:31,754 --> 01:32:35,504
Your girlfriend turned you up against us.
That's your problem.

1186
01:32:35,504 --> 01:32:37,379
That's not true!

1187
01:32:37,795 --> 01:32:39,982
It must be.
She infected you with her attitude.

1188
01:32:39,982 --> 01:32:41,231
But you can't stop us.

1189
01:32:41,753 --> 01:32:44,461
"The Wave" will roll over all of Germany!

1190
01:32:49,044 --> 01:32:53,209
Anyone who opposes us
will be washed over by "The Wave"!

1191
01:32:54,563 --> 01:32:55,917
Right on!

1192
01:32:58,834 --> 01:33:00,917
Bring that traitor up here!

1193
01:33:17,164 --> 01:33:19,977
Marco, I'll ask you in front of everyone.

1194
01:33:20,602 --> 01:33:23,309
Are you with us or against us?

1195
01:33:23,309 --> 01:33:25,080
Are you totally crazy?

1196
01:33:26,122 --> 01:33:27,580
What should we do with the traitor?

1197
01:33:29,455 --> 01:33:31,433
What should we do with the traitor?

1198
01:33:34,142 --> 01:33:35,288
Bomber, tell us!

1199
01:33:36,016 --> 01:33:37,474
Well?

1200
01:33:40,079 --> 01:33:41,641
You helped drag him up here.

1201
01:33:43,932 --> 01:33:45,599
Because you said so.

1202
01:33:45,910 --> 01:33:48,202
Because I said so?

1203
01:33:50,077 --> 01:33:52,057
Would you kill him if I said so?

1204
01:33:54,034 --> 01:33:56,951
Should we hang him or cut his head off?

1205
01:33:58,409 --> 01:34:02,680
We could torture him first,
so he agrees to our rules.

1206
01:34:04,241 --> 01:34:06,325
That's what they do in dictatorships.

1207
01:34:13,616 --> 01:34:15,281
Do you understand what happened here?

1208
01:34:17,782 --> 01:34:20,490
- You all right, Marco?
- Yeah, sure.

1209
01:34:24,864 --> 01:34:29,030
Do you remember the question
at the beginning of the week?

1210
01:34:29,863 --> 01:34:32,154
Would a dictatorship be possible again 
in Germany?

1211
01:34:34,654 --> 01:34:37,466
That's what happened here.
Fascism.

1212
01:34:40,904 --> 01:34:42,466
We thought we were special.

1213
01:34:42,986 --> 01:34:44,445
Better than the rest.

1214
01:34:45,382 --> 01:34:46,736
And what's worse...

1215
01:34:48,402 --> 01:34:51,318
we excluded others
who didn't agree with us.

1216
01:34:53,402 --> 01:34:54,652
We hurt them...

1217
01:34:57,465 --> 01:34:59,339
I don't want to think
what we might have been capable of.

1218
01:35:05,067 --> 01:35:06,629
I owe you all an apology.

1219
01:35:08,088 --> 01:35:09,129
We went too far.

1220
01:35:14,025 --> 01:35:15,274
I went too far.

1221
01:35:19,023 --> 01:35:20,378
But now it's over.

1222
01:35:21,731 --> 01:35:24,335
What's this mean?
For "The Wave"?

1223
01:35:25,272 --> 01:35:26,522
It's over.

1224
01:35:27,668 --> 01:35:28,710
Just like that?

1225
01:35:29,439 --> 01:35:31,418
Yes, just like that.

1226
01:35:32,043 --> 01:35:33,501
No, it's not over.

1227
01:35:33,813 --> 01:35:35,584
Yes Tim, it's over.

1228
01:35:36,000 --> 01:35:37,772
But not everything about "The Wave" was bad!

1229
01:35:39,125 --> 01:35:40,583
We all felt it.

1230
01:35:40,896 --> 01:35:43,291
We made mistakes, but we can fix that.

1231
01:35:43,812 --> 01:35:47,250
No, Dennis.
That kind of thing can't be fixed.

1232
01:35:49,749 --> 01:35:51,311
I want you all to go home now.

1233
01:35:52,561 --> 01:35:54,852
I'm sure you have a lot to think about.

1234
01:36:13,808 --> 01:36:15,474
- Maja, I...
- Leave me alone.

1235
01:36:19,015 --> 01:36:20,057
Stop!

1236
01:36:20,786 --> 01:36:22,974
The doors stay shut!

1237
01:36:23,598 --> 01:36:24,952
Nobody goes home!

1238
01:36:31,410 --> 01:36:33,805
- Put it down.
- You lied to us.

1239
01:36:36,721 --> 01:36:39,429
"The Wave" lives. It isn't dead!

1240
01:36:41,096 --> 01:36:44,430
Say it, "The Wave" lives!

1241
01:36:45,470 --> 01:36:47,137
It only fires blanks.

1242
01:36:56,510 --> 01:36:59,740
Now you take me seriously, huh?

1243
01:37:00,364 --> 01:37:02,447
I know you were fucking with me.

1244
01:37:04,739 --> 01:37:05,676
You all were!

1245
01:37:12,654 --> 01:37:13,696
"The Wave"...

1246
01:37:15,049 --> 01:37:16,404
was my life.

1247
01:37:22,757 --> 01:37:25,569
Tim, calm down.

1248
01:37:27,860 --> 01:37:28,902
Calm down.

1249
01:37:29,943 --> 01:37:30,985
Put the gun down.

1250
01:37:35,047 --> 01:37:37,964
Come another step closer
and I'll shoot you in the face.

1251
01:37:39,318 --> 01:37:40,359
And then what?

1252
01:37:42,338 --> 01:37:43,379
And then what?

1253
01:37:44,317 --> 01:37:47,546
There'll be no Mr Wenger,
no one to lead "The Wave".

1254
01:37:49,524 --> 01:37:51,399
Is that what you want?

1255
01:40:45,532 --> 01:40:47,628
Karo, come here.